CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 2, 1957, pg. 19, reads: "Key Win - Gerald Jackson (55) and William Gamble (57), two of the stars on Oliver High School's classy basketball team, prepare to go to the boards as Bob Backode of South Hills goes up for a jump shot. Oliver won the game and continued as favorites to win the Section 2 cage race. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Basketball game with South Hills High School player #7 Bob Backode leaping with ball, against Oliver High School, including players #55 Gerald Jackson, and #57 William Gamble, in gymnasium
